<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <!--
    Ce fichier HTML fait partie du site d'Ana Ruiz.
    Structure, navigation, et fonctionnalités sont expliquées par des commentaires dans le code.
    Tout est responsive, accessible et moderne. Voir README.md pour plus de détails.
  -->

  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sur le sentier du dragonnier (2008) - Ana Ruiz</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat+Alternates:wght@400;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style-modern.css">
  <style>
    body { background: #151516 !important; }
    .gallery-page { max-width: 1000px; margin: 5rem auto 3rem auto; padding: 0 1vw; }
    .gallery-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: #f4efe9; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.25; }
    .gallery-desc { color: #cec9c4; font-size: 1.09rem; margin: 0 0 2.2em 0; text-align: center; font-style: italic; }
    .gallery-works { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 2em 2em; margin-bottom: 2em; }
    .gallery-work { background: rgba(38,37,41,0.12); border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 2px 14px #19171b18; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; transition: box-shadow 0.16s; }
    .gallery-work img { width: 100%; height: 260px; object-fit: cover; background: #222; display: block; cursor: pointer; }
    .gallery-work-title { margin: 1em 0 0.6em 0; color: #f4efe9; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.09rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2px; text-align: center; }
    .gallery-citation { margin: 2.5em auto 1.5em auto; color: #a7a2b6; background: rgba(44,44,48,0.18); border-left: 3px solid #8b858c; font-style: italic; font-size: 1.07rem; padding: 1em 1.3em; max-width: 650px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 2px 14px #19171b18; }
    .gallery-back { display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-top: 2.5em; }
    .gallery-back a { font-size: 1rem; color: #968a7f; text-decoration: none; background: rgba(238, 233, 222, 0.12); padding: 0.7em 1.5em; border-radius: 18px; transition: background 0.14s, color 0.14s; box-shadow: 0 2px 9px #18101421; }
    .gallery-back a:hover { background: rgba(238, 233, 222, 0.22); color: #b3a797; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .gallery-title { font-size: 1.3rem;}
      .gallery-works { grid-template-columns: 1fr;}
      .gallery-work img { height: 180px;}
    }
  </style>

<style>
/* --- Correctifs mobile: signature visible, hamburger réduit, titres centrés --- */
@media (max-width: 840px){
  /* Afficher la signature en mobile et la réduire */
  .nav-signature{display:block; height:20px; width:auto; margin-left:.25rem; opacity:.95}
  .nav-signature img{height:20px; width:auto; display:block; opacity:.95}
  /* Bouton hamburger plus petit et mieux clicable */
  .hamburger{margin-left:auto; width:40px; height:36px; padding:0; display:grid; place-items:center; font-size:1rem; line-height:1; border-radius:.5rem}
  /* Menu mobile: centrer les titres et l'alignement */
  .nav-links{display:none; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; text-align:center}
  .nav-links.open{display:flex}
  .nav-links a{display:block; padding:.6rem 0; font-size:1.05rem}
}
</style>

</head>

<body>
  <!-- ===== Barre de navigation principale ===== -->

  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="navbar-container">
      <div class="nav-logo">
        <a href="index.html">Ana Ruiz</a>
        <img src="img/signature.png" alt="Signature Ana Ruiz" class="nav-signature">
      </div>
      <button id="menu-toggle" aria-label="Ouvrir le menu" class="hamburger">&#9776;</button>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="index.html">Accueil</a></li>
        <li><a href="galeries.html" class="active">Galeries</a></li>
        <li><a href="diaporama.html">Diaporama</a></li>
        <li><a href="apropos.html">À propos</a></li>
        <li><a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>
  
  <!-- ===== Contenu principal de la page ===== -->
  <main>

    <div class="gallery-page fade-in">
      <div class="gallery-title">Sur le sentier du dragonnier (2008)</div>
      <div class="gallery-desc">
        Cheminer au fil du végétal, dans l’univers mystique du dragonnier, entre mémoire et métamorphose.
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-works">

        <div class="gallery-work">
          <img src="img/dragonnier-couverture.jpg" alt="Dragonnier couverture">
          <div class="gallery-work-title">Dragonnier couverture</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-work">
          <img src="img/le-vieux-dragonnier.jpg" alt="Le vieux dragonnier">
          <div class="gallery-work-title">Le vieux dragonnier</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-work">
          <img src="img/le-vieux-volcan.jpg" alt="Le vieux volcan">
          <div class="gallery-work-title">Le vieux volcan</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-work">
          <img src="img/au-dessous-du-volcan.jpg" alt="Au-dessous du volcan">
          <div class="gallery-work-title">Au-dessous du volcan</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-work">
          <img src="img/sable-noir.jpg" alt="Sable noir">
          <div class="gallery-work-title">Sable noir</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-work">
          <img src="img/annapurna.jpg" alt="Annapurna">
          <div class="gallery-work-title">Annapurna</div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="gallery-citation">
        «&nbsp;Le sentier du dragonnier, c’est aussi le sentier de la mémoire, de la transformation...&nbsp;»
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-back">
        <a href="galeries.html">&larr; Retour aux galeries</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Lightbox pour affichage plein écran -->
  <div id="lightbox" class="lightbox">
    <span class="lightbox-close" id="lightbox-close">&times;</span>
    <img class="lightbox-img" id="lightbox-img" src="" alt="Œuvre en plein écran">
  </div>
  
  <!-- ===== Pied de page commun à tout le site ===== -->
  <footer>

    <p>&copy; 2025 Ana Ruiz. Tous droits réservés. | <a href="mentions-legales.html">Mentions légales</a></p>
  </footer>
  
  <!-- ===== Scripts spécifiques à la page ===== -->
  <script>

  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    // Ouvre lightbox au clic
    document.querySelectorAll('.gallery-work img').forEach(function(img) {
      img.addEventListener('click', function() {
        var lightbox = document.getElementById('lightbox');
        var lightboxImg = document.getElementById('lightbox-img');
        lightboxImg.src = this.src;
        lightbox.style.display = 'flex';
      });
    });
    // Ferme sur croix
    document.getElementById('lightbox-close').onclick = function() {
      document.getElementById('lightbox').style.display = 'none';
      document.getElementById('lightbox-img').src = '';
    };
    // Ferme sur clic hors image
    document.getElementById('lightbox').addEventListener('click', function(e) {
      if (e.target === this) {
        this.style.display = 'none';
        document.getElementById('lightbox-img').src = '';
      }
    });
    // Ferme sur ESC
    document.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
      if (e.key === 'Escape') {
        document.getElementById('lightbox').style.display = 'none';
        document.getElementById('lightbox-img').src = '';
      }
    });
    // Burger menu
    document.getElementById('menu-toggle').onclick = function() {
      document.querySelector('.nav-links').classList.toggle('show');
    };
    document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach(function(el) {
      el.classList.add('visible');
    });
  });
  </script>
</body>
</html>

